{"tid":101050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇做過金融既巴打解釋下點解可以呃到咁多錢","createTime":"2017-01-30T13:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T14:04:14.000Z","uid":34871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3411e1c11482f0383e9266d8f634de9e80303bb2","tid":101050,"uid":34871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:49:41.000Z","msg":"林寶跑車與七人車旺角相撞，4人受傷送院。晚上9時許，一輛林寶堅尼跑車沿旺角道西行，至香港仔魚蛋粉對開時，與一輛右轉入通菜街的七人車相撞，繼而失控撞向路中石壆，車頭凹陷損毀，車廂安全氣袋彈出，七人車則右後轆受損，意外中跑車司機、七人車3名乘客受傷，有人報警求助。救護員接報趕至，將傷者送院治理，警方正調查意外原因。 <br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署資料顯示，涉事林寶堅尼GALLARDO COUPE超級跑車於2009年出廠，當時車價約366萬港元，現時登記車主為一名姓李男子，登記地址為天水圍天逸邨。涉事本田Freed Aero七人車在前年落地，當時車價約23萬港元，車主登記地址為旺角嘉麗園。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/bkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170129%2Fbkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001.html&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=dc546520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/bkn-20170129215515539-0129_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/214921_078024aebf904ca9305c8753a401c6a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F214921_078024aebf904ca9305c8753a401c6a9.jpg&h=e4cbe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/214922_34555bc5a15d4ea5422281e77b823f69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F214922_34555bc5a15d4ea5422281e77b823f69.jpg&h=3333e569&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MQpRt6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MQpRt6.jpg&h=3d60c549&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/214925_2b420e60d4b8e8833cbbb2548c204a30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.es